  "instructions": [
    "Preheat a toaster or a non\u2011stick skillet over medium heat.",
    "In a small bowl whisk together olive oil, rosemary, thyme, smoked paprika, sea salt, black pepper, lemon zest, and balsamic vinegar until well combined.",
    "Brush each slice of bread evenly with the herb\u2011oil mixture.",
    "Toast the bread slices in the toaster or skillet until golden and crisp, about 2\u20133 minutes per side.",
    "While the toast is still hot, sprinkle grated Parmesan over each slice to create a crumbly, savory topping.",
    "Serve immediately for best crispness."
